{"tid":150011,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係好想有個家姐,有個家姐真係好好","createTime":"2017-03-09T16:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T11:41:02.000Z","uid":84102,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28a34e8f5cfb2cf80c83a120569ad4b359f6860c","tid":150011,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:46:05.000Z","msg":"細個時當我比其他細路仔恰果陣又會為我出頭教訓班壞蛋:<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當升到中學時,第一次失戀家姐又會 抱抱你 摸摸你個頭安慰你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同你講 呢個世界仲有大把好女仔值得你去愛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大學畢業後 為左慶祝你搵到第一份工,家姐又會突登去為你做一套既黑色西裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n家姐出黎做左野幾年,就算識左個男朋友,都唔會唔記得你呢個傻更更既細佬 <br />\n仲會時不時買定啲零食請你食,有時月尾見你唔夠錢駛又會靜靜雞ZIP錢落你個銀包度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出糧時仲會買一件唔好睇但係好好好貴既t-shirt比你著<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然唔好睇　但我一定會著住出街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔開心時 就會想有抱抱家姐既衝動 但係又唔會尷尬 因為你係佢既好細佬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n家姐又唔會好似出面啲女人咁 背叛你 放棄你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c53cea163612a76c58b5612823aeb16563734d1","tid":150011,"uid":13875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:47:38.000Z","msg":"啱啱訓醒?"},{"pid":"61ea3a75ab680f68e7c271ed94ec633944fbed51","tid":150011,"uid":52543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:48:16.000Z","msg":"傻啦<br />\n天下家姐一樣黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想知再講"},{"pid":"bce7ef59a2fb0f34589a4727c40b9b02c1e269b6","tid":150011,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:05:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f94dd51a0d598939d7ec37a7