:31:16.000Z","msg":"你未見識過冇拖拍發姑婆瘟既家姐"},{"pid":"eabae84d0c9497f9533b69d2435229ba1df28421","tid":150011,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:36:37.000Z","msg":"家姐我有三個<br />\n以上的事一件都無做過<br />\n對我來講家姐係仆街的代名詞<br />\n<br />\n需要隨便攞去<br />\n不設退換"},{"pid":"973a75fa9388ddebe9d83f4f9dc9e99a7de3bb73","tid":150011,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T03:36:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你未見識過冇拖拍發姑婆瘟既家姐</blockquote><br />\n唔準咁樣話家姐"},{"pid":"fed5655c2535eb685172962464a3901ff9e65ceb","tid":150011,"uid":12448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T04:58:09.000Z","msg":"送個比你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197a7b5fb590b71f08bc74676aaa2992c9dad451","tid":150011,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T07:45:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>送個比你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nokay<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e217fe9cc90eb3b87d863a021f06b89358cc3570","tid":150011,"uid":6267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T07:51:44.000Z","msg":"你諗得太多！<br />\n<br />\n除左會請你食野都冇咩，佢有男朋友你仲驚，<br />\n<br />\n佢會搵你試毒，我就係有個家姐"},{"pid":"843dd8bb36ad6ebd62872828a204569e1d34c42b","tid":150011,"uid":51697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T11:19:24.000Z","msg":"你試下有個家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申有家姐有細佬"},{"pid":"8d735273ae893e91cd764cb83ebc9529a1f6839f","tid":150011,"uid":80107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T11:41:02.000Z","msg":"FF總是美好的<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}